name: gulp-cli
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "gulp-cli" %}
{% set version = "2.3.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://registry.npmjs.org/{{ name }}/-/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tgz
  sha256: 0a5a76e5be9856edf019fb5be0ed8501a8d815da1beeb9c6effca07a93873ba4

build:
  number: 6
  skip: true  # [win]

requirements:
  host:
    - nodejs
    - yarn <2
  run:
    - nodejs

test:
  commands:
    - gulp --help

about:
  home: https://github.com/gulpjs/gulp-cli
  license: MIT
  license_file:
    - LICENSE
    - ThirdPartyLicenses.txt
  summary: Command Line Interface for gulp

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - xhochy
